&lt;h1 id=&#34;Conclusion&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Conclusion&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Conclusion&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;In my opinion, you should choose covaxin over covishield. As you have already read the differences apart from cost everything is better than covishield. I am not saying that covishield is not good or it is bad. As there is a shortage of vaccines in the country, one should get vaccinated with any one of these, but if you have choice go for Covaxin.&lt;br&gt;And I forgot to mention &lt;strong&gt;Both vaccines are capable of handling all the incoming new strains of coronaviruses&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
